+ * =============================================================================
+ * Description : Butterfly of 4 input vectors
+ * Arguments   : Inputs  - in0, in1, in2, in3
+ *               Outputs - out0, out1, out2, out3
+ * Details     : Butterfly operation
+ * Example     :
+ *               out0 = in0 + in3;
+ *               out1 = in1 + in2;
+ *               out2 = in1 - in2;
+ *               out3 = in0 - in3;
+ * =============================================================================
